law.history: Repealed 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 426, sec. 628, effective July 15, 1998; amended ch. 426, sec. 128, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 426, sec. 128, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 405, sec. 47, effective July 15, 1994. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. VI, sec. 41. -- Amended 1970 Ky. Acts ch. 180, sec. 3. -- Created 1962 Ky. Acts ch. 106, Art. IX, sec. 4.

metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/98). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 426, sec. 628 prevails over its amendment in 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 426, sec. 128.
